text: Bradley Dial (born 1 April 1995) is a South African first-class cricketer. He was part of South Africa's squad for the 2014 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup. He was included in the Gauteng cricket team squad for the 2015 Africa T20 Cup.Gauteng Squad / Players – ESPNcricinfo.
